    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GET THE FULL EXPERIENCE</h2><br>Can't get enough of Kuroi Tsubasa?<br>How about this lil' bonus content?<br><br>This DLC contains three things:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> A character model viewer in the game itself<br></li><li> Desktop Wallpapers in 4k resolution<br></li><li>An exclusive Orchestral Rendition of Kurehas theme, which you can use for Video and Stream production</li></ul><br>The Character viewer will be available from the main menu.<br><br>To access the Song and the Wallpapers you need to navigate to the game's local files.<br>To do that, follow these easy steps:<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HOW TO ACCES THE SONG AND THE WALLPAPERS</h2>First, right click on the entry of the game in your Steam library. Next, choose &quot;Properties&quot;.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810010/extras/f964831ab4947f481da4a0b2aeb75022.avif?t=1649066141\" width=358 height=198 /></span><br>After than, choose the tab &quot;Local Files&quot; and click &quot;Browse&quot; on the top right.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810010/extras/step2.1.PNG?t=1649066141\" /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810010/extras/step2.2.PNG?t=1649066141\" /></span><br>Last, doubleclick the &quot;DLC&quot; folder and enjoy your DLC goodies~<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1810010/extras/dlc.PNG?t=1649066141\" /></span>",
